config PTTTL
	bool "PTTTL/RTTTL ringtone parser and sample generator"
	help
	  Enable the eriknyquist/ptttl library (MIT). Parses RTTTL/PTTTL ringtone
	  strings and generates int16_t PCM audio samples with no dynamic memory
	  allocation. Requires only string.h (memset) and stdint.h.
